n-K\\'arm\\'an vortex street. A physical\npicture for the observed structure based on ion-drag, neutral streaming and\nelectric forces is discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Feb 2018 19:05:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Sep 2018 20:28:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-02"}
