any-sorted algebra are bisimilar. To the best of\nour knowledge, our translation and bisimilar proof is the first attempt in\ntranslating and relating an order-sorted algebra with a many-sorted one in a\nway that keeps the size of the translated many-sorted algebra relatively small.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Feb 2018 02:06:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-20"}
