. However, with the\nsample in hand, it was not possible to identify which stellar parameters cause\nthe observed Na and O bimodality and Na-O anticorrelation, suggesting that\nother stellar properties might be important besides stellar rotation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Feb 2018 14:48:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-20"}
